relation.text: Begun at the OLD BAYLEY On Wednesday Fifteenth of October , 1679
Transported . ONe of the first and most material Tryals on Wednesday
held correspondence with the most noted Theives , amongst whom one having a long time
Exploits on the Highway , being now
entered the House , and the Woman now
met with was not great . On Thursday
called Elixar Vite from one Salvator Winter
was said to be done at Whitsuntide last , and the other 6 Weeks ago
never complain 'd from Whitsuntide till about 3 Weeks ago
received sentence of Death , on Saturday 18 of October
